pr_body:
Implemented the changes mentioned [here](https://github.com/processing/processing-android/discussions/743#discussioncomment-6391252). Had to explicitly change trackable to plane for each use when changed Trackplanes to track-objects as Trackables was not able to be converted to planes  in: 
`ArrayList<Plane> trackObjects = new ArrayList<Trackables>();`
So, the best workaround I came up with was to change the Arraylist key to Trackables and make objects Plane whenever necessary.
